From b287a22eb480d96d7655528745bf0ec3000a8d8c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Amir Patel <amirpate@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Sep 2025 22:37:44 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP: wifi: ath12k: DP: Add WAR to suppress print on SKB
 clone failure

Currently on skb clone failure, log is printed on to console
with error log level, due to print flood onto colsole WDT is being
triggered.

ath12k_wifi7_ahb soc@0:wifi1@c0000000: skb clone failure link_id 0x0 vdevid 0x2
ath12k_wifi7_ahb soc@0:wifi1@c0000000: skb clone failure link_id 0x1 vdevid 0x2
ath12k_wifi7_ahb soc@0:wifi1@c0000000: skb clone failure link_id 0x0 vdevid 0x1
ath12k_wifi7_ahb soc@0:wifi1@c0000000: skb clone failure link_id 0x1 vdevid 0x1
ath12k_wifi7_pci 0001:01:00.0: skb clone failure link_id 0x0 vdevid 0x0

to address this, suppress the log level of print from err to dbg

Patch-dependency:
0478-UPSTREAM-wifi-DP-ath12k-Add-eth-offload-support-for-.patch

Fixes : I2768c6a76de813a376baaee0bfce099589010b4c
(UPSTREAM:DP:wifi: mac80211/ath12k: Add 802.3 multicast offload support)

Change-Id: I0acf8ce758c43f6059efd85de55dcca5a8bba617
Signed-off-by: Amir Patel <amirpate@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
index a229a13..6dca2e4 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
@@ -1597,7 +1597,7 @@ static void ath12k_wifi7_mac_op_tx(struct ieee80211_hw *hw,
 			if (is_eth) {
 				msdu_copied = skb_clone(skb, GFP_ATOMIC);
 				if (!msdu_copied) {
-					ath12k_err(ar->ab,
+					ath12k_dbg(ar->ab, ATH12K_DBG_MAC,
 						   "skb clone failure link_id 0x%X vdevid 0x%X\n",
 						   link_id, tmp_arvif->vdev_id);
 					continue;
-- 
2.34.1

